OL,5, A grieving woman who nursed her        
OL,6, terminally ill mum says she was denied 
OL,7, the chance to say goodbye because the  
OL,8, funeral home said the body had started 
OL,9, to decompose.                          
OL,11,FShe's one of a number of relatives who 
OL,12,Fhave spoken to BBC Radio 4 documentary 
OL,13,Fseries, File on 4, about their         
OL,14,Fexperience with Legacy Independent     
OL,15,FFuneral Directors, which is currently  
OL,16,Funder investigation by the police.     
OL,18,FThe woman, who we've called Louise to  
OL,19,Fprotect her identity, was dealt a      
OL,20,Ffurther blow when attempting to collect
OL,21,Fher mother's ashes.                    
